QUICK START:

Install Lingua::MSWordSpell by unpacking the tarball 
and running the following commands in the source directory:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install
    Then delete the source directory tree since it's no longer needed.

    run 'perldoc Lingua::MSWordSpell' to read the full documentation.

To contact the authors, send an email to:

	cpan _at_ bbc.co.uk
	
Our CPAN page is http://search.cpan.org/~bbc